i got a new journal.

its

_car_underwater

ok so today had school.

got a ninety nine on a math quiz we had before vacation.

in study hall i was in the freshman room and i wasnt giving sarah and tina liger paper and hunter walked in and was like why the hell are you in my study hall so i said because im dealing drugs. and of course the teacher walks in right as im selling that and looks at me evily. and then im like not really im just giving them papers. which also sounded bad. so i was like damnit its liger paper. screw this im gone.

then i saw josh in the hallway and told him the story. i love josh haha.

meant our mentees. mines cool.

came home.

went to work.

did air trak with randy.

hurt my knee.

planned everything for operation 0165.

then saturday im probably going to the bowling alley and sleeping over bretts house.

then sunday me and em are hopefully hanging out with joey and anthony.

anyways after work no one showed up to pick me up from work.

so i called mike and walked to dunkins since he was picking up brett and said hed pick me up.

so i went back to bretts.

had some pizza and mashed potatoes.

and chilled there with him until almost eight.

i fucking love that kid.

dad picked me up.

came home.

watching gilmore girls.

tomorrow me and whitney are supposed to hang out.

~xxx~

school was school.

marianna bought me a flower at lunch.

steve bit it. haha dork.

came home.

found out i had a staff meeting.

so i figured out ride situations for that.

mom picked me up.

went to winchednon.

got an orange mango coolata.

picked up harry.

swung by bretts new house-thing. its pretty sweet. of course michelle showed up too. but besides that yeah. im happy they have somewhere near downtown again so i can sleepover again. yay.

went to the clark.

hung out with brett at the courts.

went to the staff meeting. ill probably just do that even if i get the counciler job. which me and whitney probably wont get. but its all good.

came home.

had some fries.

the end.

~xxx~

today i went to the ecotarium with my family and my aunt and her kids. her kids are cool. theres jeff and pat who are in college and dress cooly and colleen who has cool hair and bryan whose little. anyways we walked around and what not. near the end we were under the huge tent thing. and half the poles had fallen down and what not. so harry climbed to the top and slid down. no one saw. eventually we got done with that. and harry picked up one of the fallen poles and hit another pole. well some guy who didnt even work there yelled at him and told on us. so some people who worked there came over and asked us to leave. fun.

and everything with hope/sean/joey/juston is figured out.

~xxx~

so this ..

if you read this,
even if i don't speak to you often,
you must post a memory of me.
It can be anything you want, it can be good or bad,
just so long as it happened.
Then post this to your journal. See what people remember about you...

and an update.

last night me and em went to hungry four. and we ate. then we called whitney and told her to meet us at hungry four. but we walked to her house. and it turned out she was getting a ride to hungry four so were standing in her front yard waiting to scare her as she pulls out of the driveway. she got out and we walked to dunkins even though she was supposed to be at hungry four. i got a french vanilla coffee coolata and whit got a orange-mango coolata. whitneys was better than mine. but emily ended up getting a kiddie french vanilla coolata. then my dad came and we dropped whit off and she gave me her coolata since she couldnt bring it home. dropped em. went back to dads. played poker and what not with harry dad and sam. went to bed around eleven. woke up at six thirty this morning. left to go get hunter from craigs house. met my mom there. we decided to skip hunters practice so we all went out to breakfast at friendlys with my mom and harry. then harry and mom left for harrys baseball game and me dad and hunter went over to ocean state job lot.  i got some new axe and it smells wicked good. and i got some batteries, a hello kitty mothers day card, something for adrienne, an american eagle guys t-shirt that says "take me for a ride" on it for three dollars, and some ninja turtle playing cards. then we went to leominster. i hung out with timmeh and collin for a little. not alotta people knew that the game was at ten. but eventually people showed up. me and tim did the clock. and brett gave me his sweatshirt to wear since i was freezing and didnt want to get wet. we won three to one. and bowman is expelled and we forfeited the last game because he played when he wasnt supposed to. anyways after that game i sat in the car. changed into my new shirt. took my pants off haha. i put shorts on though. and yeah i just listened to music and painted my nails and dried my clothes. harry had a game that my dad was watching. i went to go pee and i ran into the bathroom and the floor was wet so i slipped and fell. fun. then went back in the car. eventually we left for joeys. we as in me my dad and brothers. they dropped me there. it was just me and joey. and then lenny showed up with joeys mom. got a tour of the house. then left for stand out saturday at mahar. that was fun. we hung out with anthony. i kept spraying lenny with my axe and i told him it was because he smelled bad. not really though. and yeah. basically we just hung out there from like two til seven. and it was fun. i went into the boys bathroom and anthony and lenny were like what the hell. anthony tried to squeaze into a locker. but anyways after that we went to joeys and hung there until my mom came.

ok and i found the WHOLE FUCKING THING OUT. i talked to sean and joey about it and they both said you made this fucking up. so whatever were done. and brett doesnt like you so get over him.

tomorrow is mothers day. im going to the ecotarium. im going to see if joey can come.

three things:
- hunters having surgery in two weeks to have his port removed and its wicked dangerous so im scared and worried and what not.
- my grampa was in the hospital because he had pnemonia and a high fever and he has cancer so theyre not sure how much longer hell make it.
- my cousin in law is being deported to iraq for the third time. he has a daughter whose like one or two. how bad does that suck.

oh and i want to temporarily dye my hair so suggest a color. thanks loves.

~xxx~

sophmore testing is done.

its been fun.

not.

testes suck [sarah i love you haha]

tonight im going to hungry four with em for some pizza then im sleeping at my dads

tomorrow im going to some thing at mahar with joey from twelve til seven

then i have no idea

everyone loves a nerdy girl (such as moi)

and i love elmo floatation devices


eww .. have you ever seen anyone so gross looking?

that was my outfit today minus the floatie and plus joeys dickies shirt.

anyways im done annoying ya'll.

whoa i just said ya'll.

~xxx~

people suck.

yeah.

only like one person knows what im talking about.

but as soon as i found out who started this shit im done.

the next time anyone fucking brings the whole thing up im done with them.

got it?

~xxx~

ok i came home. hung out.

got a call from a telemarketer.

if you know me then you know that i feel bad about hanging up on telemarketers. so i had a three minute convo with the guy. pathetic.

then i got a call and the guy says DID I WIN? and im like umm did you win what? and hes like oh this isnt the radio station? and i said nope. he goes oh sorry and hangs up.

then i get the bright idea to make pancakes since i told everyone i would.

well i was on the phone with hope. and we three wayed brett to see how to make pancakes. he didnt know.

but it ended with three gross pancakes.

me melting the measuring cup to the bottom of the frying pan.

and me burning my hand.

great.

i got yelled at.

well i was on the phone with joey.

i have to buy my mom a new pan. and im never allowed to use the stove again.

thats pretty much it.

~xxx~

ok so jersey was love. but what happens in jersey stays in jersey. (sorry!!) but breezy collin tim craig kevin will mummy and russel and a little bit of jimmy and mike it was amazing. i love you guys!

i bought some slip on vans with pink elephants on them. and me and breezy bought matching hats to be cool like the guys. except ours are black and say c-unit hockey in hot pink and have the cyclone. and on the back mine says hooker and hers says breezy.

schools been ok. i have sophmore testing this week. im failing geography because i dont do the work. ill catch up.

the bus ride today was interesting. glenn was definately trying to get me to flash him. and he was trying to break my bracelets. he broke one. and he kept trying to grab my chest. and then he was trying to pull the cooper-candy scence in the hot tub from euro trip. yeah thats definately not where he parked his car. oh and i forgot my jacket and was freezing so adam made me wear his. and yeah i was just takling with glenn adam and josh the whole time. pretty sweet. i was sitting on the back part of the seat for a while.

tomorrow is thursday so i get to see joey and hope.

last night me and sarah went to bretts hockey game. it was fun. i hung out with timmy. we won. oh and brett came to my work so i could give him his present from jersey (skateboarding is not a crime t-shirt, postcard, and fake bling bling) and hope swung by with a note. i saw whitney and brett hueghy. pretty cool.

im making pancakes tomorrow morning. yumm.

i cant really remember any of the awesome stuff i was going to write. oh well.

i love cyclones hockey.

~xxx~

ok so went to winchendon to drop moms car to get fixed.

mike was supposed to pick us up. but he was late. so we walked to dunkins in the rain.

i got a lemonade coolata and a bagle.

ran to family dollars.

bought a disposable camera and some batteries.

talked to lisa may.

walked back to dunkins.

ran into mr harvey.

he took me to go see adrienne.

i met her mega ultra cool friends.

i think i scared them.

we watched lacrosse. in the rain. fun. i like lacrosse.

then we went back to dunkins but my mom had left but we saw her across the street. they dropped me with her.

hunter got his hair cut.

we walked to get the car.

went to bretts.

found out harrys baseball game was cancelled.

kidnaped brett.

after he molested me with his new skateboard.

went to wendys in gardner.

i bought him dinner.

then we went to harrys street hockey game.

i played soccer with brett in the rain.

then hunters game.

chilled with mummy derek tim and kevin.

my dad showed up.

hes giving me money for jersey.

we lost.

found out will isnt playing b.

came home.

found out mike isnt playing b.

so im all pissed.

because we have like no b players.

and mikes being all gay about it.

and his moms my ride in jersey.

but at least ill still have everyone to hang out with.

me and breezy declared well make it fun.

i promised brett id buy him something.

because i love him.

but yeah the whole cylones thing is confusing right now and i dont feel like explaining but the only people who it concerns know the whole deal.

tomorrow is work then youth group to see my joey.

and its payday.

i need lotso money for this weekend.

i cant wait to get to jersey and spend the whole weekend with breezy.

im just so pissed with whats going on.

and jack and bobby was good tonight. sad. but good.

and im pissed.

the end.

~xxx~

because im paranoid and pessimistic

gah i suck

and what if everything i have is just a lie

i want to talk about this

to someone

why does everyone have to be in school

i need reassurance

i need to figure this out

and i need to know why

and i want to know that everything is fine

and that my mind is just making up all this stuff

because i dont want to lose you again

no it cant happen

ill figure this out

~xxx~

nothing much has happened lately. sarah slept over sunday night and then again last night. today is her birthday. and i have work later on today. i need to go to wal mart so i can buy a portable dvd player for new jersey. we leave on friday morning and im staying with the macmillans since i dont want to stay with my family in a different hotel.

i love the lake.


the docks being over taken by waves.

pretty water.

ok friday night sarah and marianna stopped by at my house and we walked down to dunkins and i got a lemonade coolata since those things are awesome. and hunter and craig met us there and we all walked home together. sarah danced in the middle of the road. then i hung out after they left until adrienne came and picked me up at like eight fifteen or so. we went to the movies to see a lot like love at nine thirty five. we got there early. her dad bought my ticket and he told me that he thinks im a good friend. i wore soccer shorts over my jeans, adrienens "blondes do it better shirt", my "i only date crack whores" hat and a heart painted on my face. i was so hott. so me and adrienne ran over to the dollar tree before it closed. i bought a water noodle, an elmo water tube, some glow sticks, chap stick, yumumy lipgloss, a pretty bracelet, some eyeshadow, batteries, hand sanitizer and some more lipgloss. then we went to the movie. and it was good. i laughed and cried. and ashton kutcher is hot. after the movie while we were waiting for adhds dad we chilled with stef lafrienne and her friends. then adhds dad dropped me off at maybe twelve thirty or so. i went to bed. then saturday i woke up at sixish. got ready to go. went to hockey. hung out with mummy. im staying with them in jersey since my moms gay and is staying at the same hotel as the red wings. after that we went to the mall and me and hunter stayed and had lunch at friendlys. then we went and got emily. and shopped for a little. i bought sarahs birthday present from spencers. i got her a bear doing a sheep in the ass and boxers that say blow me on them. fun fun. then i bought a skirt from aeropostale. then we met joey and anthony and hung out with them. we saw adrienne and i gave her a hug since i love her. they ate lunch and im retarted. a conversation between me and anthony:
-me: what are you getting for lunch?
-anthony: i dont know.
-me: while theres only four choices it cant be that hard to choose.
-anthony: yes it is because theres four choices. itd be easier if there was one.
-me: ok well get mcdonalds because its cheap.
-anthony: are you saying im cheap?
-me: argh no. fine get subway because its healthy.
-anthony: are you calling me unhealthy?
-me: no. fine just get sbarros. theres nothing wrong with pizza.
-anthony: but what if its greasy?
-me: then wipe the grease off with napkins.
-anthony: but then what will i do with the napkins? will the be greasy? will i have to touch them?
-me: oh my god ill throw them away for you.
-anthony: im not even hungry.
that was the end of that. me and emily high fived eachother with chips in our hands. smart idea. we went to olympia sports to find a hat for joey. didnt find one. but we found some sexy spiked hats. then we went down to spencers. then we decided to run to toys r us in the rain. i was wearing sandals and socks. fun. when we got to toys r us i just threw away my socks. we just hung out there for a while. i saw a bird flying around but no one believed me. eventually everyone else saw it too. and we told the manager. and he told us he knew but that if we could get it out hed give us all ten dollar gift certificates. anthony made bird calls. then we played around with light sabers. joey bought a yo yo. me emily and anthony bought joey rainbow brite party hats and blow toys. we didnt tell him though. and i tried to give them to anthony behind my back and it looked funny. but after that we ran over to filenes. took pictures with random hats on. went upstairs. hid from joey so we could put on the hats and use the blowers. then we found him and made him wear them. and some lady who worked there came up to us and we thought she was going to yell at us. but she didnt. she just talked to us and asked us all the questions. and eventually we gave her a hat and blower and went back downstairs. anthony posed with a manican. and i told them we could get to the mall through filenes and they were like no. but yeah we could. so hah they lost. then we went down to fye and had some more random poses. then we went over to circuit city. and then we left. and we formed the rainbow brite club of america. and ginger ale is the official drink. anthonys the president im the vice president joeys the treasurer and emilys the secretary of defense. then we went back to joeys. and had some pizza and watched movies. and all i can say about that is rawr im a dinosaur. most random thing ever. and yes of course im the one who said it. me and em had to leave at seven fourty five. we went home and called them since i missed joey. and anthony likes emily. me and emily had ice cream and ginger ale. and my dad and sam left for work. so we watched tv and went to bed around midnight. woke up a little after nine. we were the only ones awake. hung out. played on the computer. etc etc. she left around eleven. and i watched look whose talking now and home alone three. and my dad left. same eventually woke up. i went outside and took some awesome pictures of the lake and my backyard. then sam drove me home. sarah and emma stopped in so i could give sarah her present. and then they left after an hour i think. and i started to clean. but then i just put together a really hot outfit and uploaded pictures and other unimportant stuff. but yeah now sarahs coming over soon and shes sleeping over since were on vacation and youre not. fun fun. ill post pictures after.

~xxx~

What's Your True Birth Month?

thursday - had school. went to work. missy was there since sara had to leave for florida. the kids were being awful. and juston showed up. yeah i was pretty much crying because i didnt want to talk to him or see him. and he stood in the door for atleast fifteen minutes. and i had to stay all class since missy takes forever. went to youth group and hung out with joey. dropped hope off. went to my dads. slept there.
friday - had no school. hung out all morning. went up to my school for hunters tennis practice and i skateboarded for a little. i got my ollie. sweet deal. went home. made plans to chill with adrienne. went over her house late. we chilled then snuck out.
Hell yes.

Who sneaks out on a friday night to go play tennis?

Me and adrienne.

And what do i wear?

Monkey boxers, soccer socks, and a tie around my head.

Were pretty damn cool.

And i suck at tennis.

But i like playing on playgrounds at ten at night.

And all the "cool" kids hang out at the courts.

Pssh who likes cool kids anyways?

Im the only cool kid in winchendon.

You know it.

I like it.

You like it.

We saw a skunk.

And adrienne layed in the middle of the highway.

then we went home pretty late. thirty i think it was. watched bridget jones diary. adrienne fell asleep. i fell asleep.
saturday - rearranged adriennes room. i like it. played mind games with her dad. emily came over. we went to the cyclones hockey game. we lost. i think. dont remember. but i saw mummy. and mikey. and jimmy. and joan. and timmy. and craigy. and kevin. and i met mikes girlfriend steph and breezys friends emma and space. but breezys in france. after the game me and em and adhd went over joeys house and hung out with all his cool friends. played texas hold em or whatever. and i won three dollars. then there was dancing around the fire. and people falling in the fire. but it wasnt me. stayed there until nine thirty or so. dad dropped em and adhd off. went home and slept.
sunday - didnt do anything.
monday - school. went over sarahs. helped her decorate her new room. walked to dunkin donuts which was a two mile walk. iick. then we managed to bum a ride off someone. she snuck around her neighbors yard. his name is bob. he drink alotta beer. and likes naked ladies. when we got a ride home the person driving almost ran over sarahs neighbor. he asked if he could help us. and i was like yeah we live there and pointed at sarahs house. i had dinner at her house. potatoes chicken and brocolli. yumm. we danced to cheesey music. scary monsters in her closet. came home at eight.
tuesday - school. then went to the clark for my interview. then hung out until my mom came. went to hunters hockey game. awesome awesome game. mike got kicked out for hitting amanda. me and jimmy almost got thrown out because we were talking back to the ref. and amanda and bagels got thrown out. but i had lotsa fun. and we won. but mikeys  suspended for three games. holy shit. after that i came home. ooh fun. brett slept over. even though i hate him.
wednesday - school. came home. hung out with brett. waited for joey and john and ginny to come over. had a waterballoon fight with brett. more of him kicking my ass with water balloons. i was soo soaked. fun times. then everyone came over. and we watched movies. and john is cool. and he thinks emilys hot. and we walked to dunkin donuts in the rain. and i got a strawberry coolata and it was iicky. came back home and watched some of water boy. brett and ginny left. my mom came home. so me john and joey went into my room and watched jack and bobby. joey hates that show haha. they left around ten. and john said he wanted to go on the roof of my trailer and if it broke he could just use paper mache. then he asked which door went to the basement. and everything is groady even if groady means boobs in german.
thursday - school. after school i went down to the clark to hang out with emily whitney and brianna. we went to brooks and bought joey a birthday card and some take five candy bars. and then we walked back to the clark. and em and whit left. and then bri left. and me and hope went to youth group. and it was joeys birthday. and he cut his hair. he doesnt like it. but yeah youth group was cool. we played musical chairs which i suck at. and we had cake and me and hope shoved our faces in it. hung out for a while. then left. dropped hope off. dad picked up brett and dropped us off at stateline with my mom. we came home. i went to bed.
today - had school. it was earth day. fun fun. nothing really exciting except for my fall. and im on vacation now. and so far it sucks balls. i want to hang out with joey tonight. or adrienne and brianna. and breezy gets back from paris today. sweet deal. and jersey is next weekend.

oh i got my report card on friday -
algebra two honors - B
economics - A
spanish - A-
english - B-
biology - A
geography - A

not too shabby. the As might be messed up though. i mean like some of them might be As instead of A-s or vice verca. anyways that is all for now. and i shall write from now on.

~xxx~

i definately took a face plant today.

right before economics.

i was walking towards the door and carolyn (sp) wasnt watching where she was going and i soo tripped over her.

face plant right into the economics room.

i wacked my hand/arm on the table then floor.

i laughed my ass off.

carolyn felt bad.

everyone laughed.

i couldnt get up.

joe was like loser get up.

i got up.

went to the nurse.

got some ice.

went back to the nurse like four times.

yeah it hurts that bad.

i cant pinch.

but it was a classic sarah move.

the end of that story.

i miss you already.

~xxx~

Around the corner I have a friend,

              In this great city that has no  end,  

             Yet the  days go by and weeks rush on, 

                 And before I know it, a year is gone.

                 And I never see my old friends face,

                For life is a swift and terrible  race,

                He knows I  like him just as well,

                 As in the days when I rang his bell.

                 And he rang mine but we were younger then,

                 And now we are busy, tired  men.

                Tired of  playing a foolish game,

                 Tired of trying to make a name.

                 "Tomorrow" I say! "I will call on Jim

                 Just to show that I'm thinking of  him."

                But  tomorrow comes and tomorrow goes,

                 And distance between us grows and grows.

               Around the corner, yet miles  away,

        "Here's a  telegram sir," "Jim died today."

           And that's what we get and deserve in the  end.

                Around the  corner, a vanished friend.

Remember to always say what you mean.
If you love someone, tell them.
Don't be afraid to express  yourself.
Reach  out and tell someone what they mean to you.
Because when you decide that it is the right time it might be too  late. 
Seize the day. Never have  regrets.
And  most importantly, stay close to your friends and family, for they have  helped make you  the person that you are today.
